{"tid":28642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依加d大學生考試衰左瀨老師","createTime":"2016-12-08T05:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T08:16:15.000Z","uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5448fe7a3bb03287f167598df3e7d4296e61c85","tid":28642,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭巴士，聽到有個大學生講電話（從佢口中聽到）<br />\n<br />\n大學生：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（無關痛癢既事省略）.. 嘩，我覺得真係好唔公平囉，有冇可能你考卷一個陣唔提我地仲有5分鐘架，佢擺明就故意唔提啦，真係好唔公平囉。仲有呀，佢比d指示好唔清楚囉，d英文唔咸唔淡咁，我係西人學生實比佢玩死。最慘係，佢考試模式居然冇講過囉，玩野咩。<br />\n<br />\n佢有d邏輯都好好笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：中六？中六好細個姐，仲係細路仔，year 1? 咁好大個啦 ，成熟過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f868e0aff81a28a31b179a77ccbf8858fc0890dc","tid":28642,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75fb0ccf24ee5b3db874c5e4bcb203358d8ec787","tid":28642,"uid":53426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a105bcf8609c2f492f5d77835add588477986fca","tid":28642,"uid":11950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>建議樓主讀下書先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d38709031af2dfb200f5f9af87868a77a5e497","tid":28642,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議樓主讀下書先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>